Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.88,0:00:29.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,翔龍子大人 請等一等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.09,0:00:31.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,飛啊 飛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.84,0:00:33.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不用擔心 武寶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.10,0:00:36.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我和火美子玩一會就回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.01,0:00:38.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,飛啊 飛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.72,0:00:40.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行啊 翔龍子大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.27,0:00:45.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,火美子 要抓緊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.94,0:00:47.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.94,0:00:51.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,翔龍子大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.41,0:01:01.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,翔龍子大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.67,0:01:08.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,翔龍子大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.22,0:01:15.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,翔龍子大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.43,0:01:22.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原諒我 武寶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.90,0:01:31.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,翔翔 再飛快一點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.40,0:01:32.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.51,0:01:57.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(200,300)}—\h沒有終結之時的物語\h—
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.39,0:02:04.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(150,1000)}救世主 再臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.40,0:02:12.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,翔龍子大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.40,0:02:15.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,翔龍子大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.37,0:02:19.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請回來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.21,0:02:27.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,終於走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.88,0:02:31.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若被武寶發現 一定會被帶回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.46,0:02:35.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,躲在這裡就沒問題了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.05,0:02:37.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒問題沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.22,0:02:43.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎…怎麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.98,0:02:45.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好像有什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.56,0:02:47.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.52,0:02:48.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等等 火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.65,0:02:53.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玩捉迷藏啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.57,0:02:56.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快回來 火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.49,0:03:00.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咦 這是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.51,0:03:24.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.32,0:03:33.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.65,0:03:39.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡 你又打瞌睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.03,0:03:40.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我沒有睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.82,0:03:43.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那你在幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.70,0:03:45.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我做了個奇怪的夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.70,0:03:48.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這不是在睡嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.00,0:03:52.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你啊 明年就要升六年級了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.00,0:03:54.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還不用功的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.59,0:03:57.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到頭來吃苦的是老師還是渡呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.43,0:04:02.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想什麼想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.18,0:04:05.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,算了 回答這個問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.06,0:04:08.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,當氣溫升到30攝氏度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.23,0:04:10.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,地面的溫度會怎樣上升
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.90,0:04:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,畫出來看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.83,0:04:27.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,創界山…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.00,0:04:33.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快醒醒 渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.34,0:04:42.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有種不祥的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.39,0:04:46.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,難道創界山發生了什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.83,0:05:12.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.84,0:05:23.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,果然 創界山果然有事發生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.22,0:05:27.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他是傻子嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.10,0:05:30.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若創界山發生什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.89,0:05:32.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他們應該會來接我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.02,0:05:42.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龍神丸 我在這裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.83,0:05:51.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對了 不來的話就由我呼叫它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.66,0:05:52.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.79,0:05:57.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龍神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.13,0:06:04.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.34,0:06:08.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼不來接我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.11,0:06:25.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這個水池不許釣魚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.66,0:06:27.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,會受罰的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.49,0:06:29.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我沒有放餌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.04,0:06:38.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有什麼煩惱嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.09,0:06:43.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在呼叫龍神大人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.59,0:06:46.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才沒有呼叫呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.09,0:06:48.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.69,0:07:02.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龍神丸?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.08,0:07:13.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龍神丸?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.00,0:07:16.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是龍神丸嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.29,0:07:22.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是龍神丸吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.84,0:07:25.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟然化成老頭子 有一手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.34,0:07:26.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真像 真像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.01,0:07:29.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,櫻花…沒有開呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.60,0:07:33.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,夏天當然不會開花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.56,0:07:40.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是 就算是春天這櫻樹也多年未開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.65,0:07:46.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,最近守護龍神大人的小孩越來越少了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.07,0:07:50.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這櫻樹是龍的化身啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.45,0:07:52.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龍的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.33,0:07:55.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你知道嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.70,0:07:59.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在天國有一個專門飼養龍的民族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.37,0:08:03.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他們能騎著龍並自在的操縱龍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.59,0:08:04.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,騎著龍?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.13,0:08:08.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,從那一族中生出住在地上的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.93,0:08:14.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,代代都把第一個出生的男孩作為守護龍神的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.93,0:08:19.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,每個男孩都取相同的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.06,0:08:22.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那名字是Adaru
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.27,0:08:24.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Adaru?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.15,0:08:31.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,永遠的生命 沒有終結之時的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.82,0:08:33.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Adaru
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.49,0:08:38.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個子孫現在應該還在某處生存
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.54,0:08:40.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那孩子能騎龍嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.54,0:08:46.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,當然 還能前往神的國度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.34,0:08:48.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,騎著龍?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.43,0:08:56.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要還持有信賴之心和巨大的夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.93,0:09:00.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,信賴之心和巨大的夢想…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.85,0:09:06.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的夢想已變得這麼小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.98,0:09:09.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再也去不了了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.99,0:09:17.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,創界山逐漸崩潰…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.37,0:09:20.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不可能有這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.33,0:09:23.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一定是心理作用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.17,0:09:29.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一定不會有事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.89,0:09:36.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.39,0:09:41.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,騙人的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.45,0:10:45.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,櫻花開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.47,0:10:59.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是天馬?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.43,0:11:01.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好疼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.64,0:11:02.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是夢啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.64,0:11:07.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.66,0:11:20.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虎王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.95,0:11:21.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.74,0:11:23.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虎王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.29,0:11:26.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是做夢吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.79,0:11:28.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 真的是本少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.46,0:11:30.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是 為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.75,0:11:32.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼本少爺會來這裡嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.30,0:11:35.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 發生了什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.76,0:11:37.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,創界山有危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.34,0:11:40.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,魔界的人又開始行動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.76,0:11:41.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,果然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.97,0:11:43.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,詳情情形之後再說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.81,0:11:47.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在快跟本少爺去創界山吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.81,0:11:48.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,騎這匹馬?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.02,0:11:49.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.94,0:11:50.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.98,0:11:52.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,願意來嗎 渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.65,0:11:53.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.61,0:11:56.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣的渡才是本少爺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.11,0:11:58.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好朋友 對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.70,0:12:00.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.49,0:12:03.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,出發了 渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.74,0:12:04.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.85,0:12:33.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡 起來 快起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.86,0:12:39.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好爽快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.28,0:12:44.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好爽快好爽快 爽快爽快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.33,0:12:45.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.20,0:12:48.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡 好久不見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.66,0:12:50.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那這裡是創界山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.33,0:12:52.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虎王呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.67,0:12:53.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,老虎在嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.05,0:12:57.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在哪裡在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.34,0:12:59.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,老虎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.55,0:13:02.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真奇怪 明明是一起來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.58,0:13:35.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,與我腦海中浮現的創界山一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.76,0:13:40.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,過來啊 鳥先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.67,0:13:41.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那不是鳥先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.23,0:13:55.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡 是渡嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.97,0:13:58.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龍神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.27,0:14:00.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡 你終於來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.40,0:14:03.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但你是怎麼來神部界的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.07,0:14:05.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是虎王帶我來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.78,0:14:09.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龍神丸 到底發生了什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.83,0:14:12.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,通往魔界的門開始打開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.00,0:14:13.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,門?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.00,0:14:16.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,從魔界吹來一股邪惡的能量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.67,0:14:19.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,使創界山變成了這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.13,0:14:21.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若門完全打開的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.09,0:14:25.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,創界山就會完全崩潰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.47,0:14:30.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鳥先生啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.10,0:14:32.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是魔界的傢伙 小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.77,0:14:36.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龍神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.86,0:14:39.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.65,0:14:41.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鳥先生 鳥先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.07,0:14:44.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龍神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.57,0:14:46.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,放開我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.62,0:14:49.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.62,0:14:52.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,放開我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.46,0:15:03.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.55,0:15:06.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.09,0:15:11.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龍神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.94,0:15:18.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼龍神丸不來?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.08,0:15:31.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.24,0:15:34.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡 是鳥先生啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.79,0:15:36.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我說過不是鳥先生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.38,0:15:45.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,剛才半信半疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.84,0:15:48.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原來果真是渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.59,0:15:49.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,古拿瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.22,0:15:50.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,果然是鳥先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.22,0:15:55.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你一直保持鳥的模樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.64,0:15:57.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣比較適合我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.39,0:15:58.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.48,0:16:02.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.52,0:16:03.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海火子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.69,0:16:07.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡 真的是渡嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.99,0:16:08.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.91,0:16:10.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣就全員到齊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.16,0:16:11.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.87,0:16:14.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,劍部武一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.91,0:16:17.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,駕到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.50,0:16:18.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,師傅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.67,0:16:20.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什…什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.33,0:16:24.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,來啊 儘管放馬過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.09,0:16:26.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,師傅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.64,0:16:36.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.77,0:16:40.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只是暫時撤退 很快就會捲土重來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.10,0:16:42.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,噢 渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.31,0:16:43.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,師傅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.69,0:16:45.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你終於來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.94,0:16:49.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,下次那些傢伙再來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.82,0:16:52.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們就呼叫魔神收拾他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.41,0:16:56.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,呼叫不了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.12,0:17:00.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,魔界的力量使魔神全動不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.25,0:17:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為魔界之門已打開了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.54,0:17:04.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.59,0:17:09.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,封印大門的"聖龍之勾玉"被魔界的人搶走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.55,0:17:11.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,"聖龍之勾玉"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.64,0:17:16.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那只要把那個"聖龍之勾玉"取回來就行了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.31,0:17:20.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雖說如此 但我們到不了魔界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.94,0:17:22.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也沒有足夠的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.47,0:17:52.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.07,0:18:08.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.45,0:18:13.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,古拿瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.53,0:18:14.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.66,0:18:19.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.92,0:18:29.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,野牛武一郎流 交叉字斬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.63,0:18:31.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,受死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.72,0:18:35.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.76,0:18:38.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.64,0:18:39.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.68,0:18:40.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,師傅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.35,0:18:42.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.15,0:18:54.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.49,0:18:56.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龍神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.66,0:19:01.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龍神丸不能來救我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.75,0:19:04.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,古拿瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.50,0:19:11.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎樣才能打倒它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.76,0:19:14.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別怕 渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.51,0:19:16.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虎王!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.30,0:19:19.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有本少爺在你身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.30,0:19:21.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在哪 虎王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.02,0:19:26.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虎王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.35,0:19:29.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要戰鬥到底 渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.61,0:19:32.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.28,0:19:35.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.70,0:19:41.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.88,0:19:49.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.22,0:20:05.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,趁現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.04,0:20:26.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.71,0:20:32.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我就是閻羅王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.67,0:20:34.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,閻羅王!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.34,0:20:37.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你就是救世主渡嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.67,0:20:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,正是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.38,0:20:42.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能接住吼鬼的劍 真了不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.76,0:20:46.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不會讓你們這些魔界中人為所欲為的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.98,0:20:52.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟把我和剛才與你交手的魔物相提並論
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.86,0:20:54.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太令我困擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.40,0:20:55.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.53,0:20:58.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在我先留你小命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.07,0:21:06.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,救世主究竟有何能耐 我會拭目以待的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.04,0:21:09.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想逃嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.96,0:21:13.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好好珍惜生命吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.05,0:21:21.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.18,0:21:23.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.72,0:21:25.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒事吧 渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.10,0:21:25.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.06,0:21:28.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個人自稱閻羅王啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.98,0:21:31.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全身散發出可怕的殺氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.94,0:21:34.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,魔界的大人物終於登場了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.65,0:21:39.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過渡擋住它的劍的時候 我真吃了一驚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.03,0:21:42.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也沒想到自己能做到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.28,0:21:45.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是虎王救了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.49,0:21:47.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對了 虎王在哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.58,0:21:55.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,靈魂出竅?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.04,0:21:57.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.21,0:22:02.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,翔龍子大人被魔界的邪氣擊中後就變成這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.89,0:22:08.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看來虎王好像掙脫了翔龍子大人的身體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.47,0:22:11.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那虎王現在在哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.27,0:22:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就沒人知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.94,0:22:16.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果渡遇見的虎王就是從
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.73,0:22:19.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,翔龍子大人體內掙脫的虎王的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.15,0:22:22.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看來除非虎王重迴翔龍子大人體內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.74,0:22:26.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,否則翔龍子大人便不會醒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.29,0:22:35.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在天部界有一顆"劍龍之勾玉"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.67,0:22:38.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若要關上魔界之門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.38,0:22:42.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,除了以"劍龍之勾玉"封印外別無他法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.97,0:22:43.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,天部界?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.18,0:22:46.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是比星界山更高的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.97,0:22:48.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,救世主渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.10,0:22:53.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你能到天部界把"劍龍之勾玉"取回來嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.31,0:22:55.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是 我一定盡力而為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.56,0:22:57.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,話雖如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.77,0:23:04.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但別說現生界 就連神部界的人也不能進入天部界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.36,0:23:09.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一進去就會觸到大龍光帝的逆鱗而喪命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.16,0:23:12.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即使如此也別無他法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.12,0:23:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若由創界山的神子告知神部界的危機的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.75,0:23:23.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大龍光帝也一定會接受的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.63,0:23:25.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是翔龍子大人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.43,0:23:28.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如今翔龍子去不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.01,0:23:31.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,身為星界山神子的海火子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.35,0:23:33.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這項使命就拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.48,0:23:38.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是 可是有上天部界的方法嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.35,0:23:41.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要利用創界山彩虹的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.11,0:23:45.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請等一下 這樣會令創界山的彩虹消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.65,0:23:50.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,彩虹消失的話 創界山就會立刻落入魔界手中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.62,0:23:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不僅如此 連聖龍妃大人的生命也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.04,0:24:00.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即使如此 也非去不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.72,0:24:10.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一定會把"劍龍之勾玉"取回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:56.97,0:25:00.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡 不論何時我都與你同在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:01.35,0:25:02.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拜託你了 渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:13.53,0:25:16.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不會讓你得逞的 救世主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:17.41,0:25:18.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,走吧 吼鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:24.92,0:25:26.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡 海火子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:30.13,0:25:32.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,聖龍妃大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:14.88,0:26:20.86,jpoped,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(150,150)}耳をふさいでも 聞こえていたの
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:21.82,0:26:28.03,jpoped,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(150,150)}時の砂が落ちる音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:30.16,0:26:36.37,jpoped,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(150,150)}黃昏に金の雲を残して
